PrecisAmendment to the UNEMPLOYMENT INSURANCE (COLLECTION OF PREMIUMS) REGULATIONS providing that disability related benefits received by an employer are not included in insurable earnings to the extent they are excluded from income by reason of subsection 6(16) of the Income Tax Act.
